# 📊 Amazon Sales Performance Dashboard

## 🔹 Overview

This project analyzes Amazon sales data (₹78M+ revenue) to uncover key business insights related to revenue trends, order performance, and operational efficiency. The results are presented through an interactive Power BI dashboard.

---

## 🔹 Objective

The goal of this project is to transform raw sales data into meaningful insights that can support data-driven decision-making and improve business performance.

---

## 🔹 Key Insights

* Over **85% of orders were successfully fulfilled**, indicating strong operational performance
* **Cancellation rate below 10%**, highlighting efficient order management
* **Consistent monthly revenue trends**, showing stable business performance
* Identified **high-performing product categories and sales patterns**

