---

## 🔹 How to Use

1. Open the `.pbix` file in Power BI Desktop to explore the dashboard
2. View the notebook for step-by-step data analysis
3. Use filters and visuals in the dashboard to interact with the data

---

## 🔹 Conclusion

This project demonstrates an end-to-end data analysis workflow — from data cleaning and exploration to visualization and insight generation — helping convert raw data into actionable business insights.

